#. Autoplay
#: src/Widgets/PreferencesPopover.vala:46
msgid "Auto-play last station on startup"
msgstr "Lecture auto dernière station au démarrage"

#: src/Widgets/PreferencesPopover.vala:48
msgid ""
"If enabled, when Tuner starts it will automatically start to play the last "
"played station"
msgstr ""
"Si activé, lorsque Tuner démarre, il commencera automatiquement à lire la "
"dernière station lue"

#. Start on Starred
